rows.label: tlk70000064_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Punpun heard from adventuring
friends that Iira now has
mighty-fighty resistance force!

rows.label: tlk70000064_02_msg0002
rows.name:
Other rumors say force is made up
of fighters from different countries.
Leader is Prince of Iira!

rows.label: tlk70000064_02_msg0003
rows.name:
A bit like friends here now.
Friends are people of many
different countries, right?

rows.label: tlk70000064_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Perhaps friends are something to
do with resistance forces...?
